  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/9384ab78d917def11ed52b2ba510efb8.avif?t=1741735653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras_big/9384ab78d917def11ed52b2ba510efb8.avif?t=1741735653 width=800 height=218 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/f285c629b4a7f269e416321c9bf28ced.webp?t=1741735653\" width=620 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you wanna walk the streets of Barcelona while looking for cute kitties from other video games? You’ve come to the right place! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Catcelona Indies' Special edition 2025</i> offers the possibility to do both. Barcelona is the scenery of this hidden object story, where you need to find los of cats (and maybe some other creatures...) and guide them to their safe place, their shelter. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All cats are randomized, so you can play endless games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/5d543f9038a8c1439598bcdea710c682.poster.avif?t=1741735653\" width=640 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/5d543f9038a8c1439598bcdea710c682.webm?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/5d543f9038a8c1439598bcdea710c682.mp4?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/2dc71b75da0cab43dc7ce08d4baafc83.webp?t=1741735653\" width=620 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All our cats come from other Indie video games. We wanted to celebrate their existence by creating a game in their honor. So you'll be able to see your favourite characters hidden here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/f406d0e4d0e3e63d050ccdafc436e87f.webp?t=1741735653\" width=620 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Barcelona offers tons of amazing places, some of them sure you have already heard about, but others we hope to surprise you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/7369771fcab4cce1484af1053c32cf38.poster.avif?t=1741735653\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/7369771fcab4cce1484af1053c32cf38.webm?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/7369771fcab4cce1484af1053c32cf38.mp4?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/b294c3f455107ee85cd943e224faf2fb.webp?t=1741735653\" width=620 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And what about sound? Oh, sound is so amazing and powerful! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’ve teamed up with Dash Obradors and lots of places have sounds, so click all over and discover them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/74ed38696eb503874a4cc50f22655398.poster.avif?t=1741735653\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/74ed38696eb503874a4cc50f22655398.webm?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/74ed38696eb503874a4cc50f22655398.mp4?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
