m/apps/2948230/extras/2dc71b75da0cab43dc7ce08d4baafc83.webp?t=1741735653\" width=620 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All our cats come from other Indie video games. We wanted to celebrate their existence by creating a game in their honor. So you'll be able to see your favourite characters hidden here!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/f406d0e4d0e3e63d050ccdafc436e87f.webp?t=1741735653\" width=620 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Barcelona offers tons of amazing places, some of them sure you have already heard about, but others we hope to surprise you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/7369771fcab4cce1484af1053c32cf38.poster.avif?t=1741735653\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/7369771fcab4cce1484af1053c32cf38.webm?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/7369771fcab4cce1484af1053c32cf38.mp4?t=1741735653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948230/extras/b294c3f455107ee85cd943e224faf2fb.webp?t=1741735653\" width=620 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And what about sound? Oh, sound is so amazing and powerful! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’ve teamed up with Dash Obradors and lots of places have sounds, so click all over and discover them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"